QueryCallback.name: CheckTestingPreConditionsEvent
QueryCallback.whereClause: JUVENILE_ID=? AND CASEFILE_ID=cast(? as INTEGER) AND ASSESSMENTTYPE=? order by createdate desc

QueryCallback.name: CheckPreConditionsForJuvenileEvent
QueryCallback.whereClause: JUVENILE_ID=? AND ASSESSMENTTYPE=? order by createdate desc offset 0 rows fetch next 1 ROW ONLY

QueryCallback.name: GetRecentRiskAnalysisForJuvenileEvent
QueryCallback.whereClause: JUVENILE_ID=? AND ASSESSMENTTYPE=? AND (DATEENTERED > getDate() - 30) order by createdate desc offset 0 rows fetch next 1 ROW ONLY

QueryCallback.name: GetRecentReferralRiskAnalysisByDateEvent
QueryCallback.whereClause: JUVENILE_ID=? AND ASSESSMENTTYPE=? AND (? > DATEENTERED) order by createdate desc offset 0 rows fetch next 1 ROW ONLY

QueryCallback.name: GetRecentRiskAnalysisForJuvenileUpTo10DaysEvent
QueryCallback.whereClause: JUVENILE_ID=? AND ASSESSMENTTYPE=? AND (DATEENTERED > getDate() - 10) order by createdate desc offset 0 rows fetch next 1 ROW ONLY

QueryCallback.name: GetLatestRiskAnalysisEvent

QueryCallback.name: GetRiskAnalysisByCasefileIdAndAssmtTypeEvent
QueryCallback.whereClause: CASEFILE_ID=cast(? as INTEGER) AND ASSESSMENTTYPE=? order by createdate desc
